long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the serene power of Satoru Gojo Moon Glow Live Wallpaper, where his mystical energy shines under a glowing moon on your Chrome new tab.

The Satoru Gojo Moon Glow Live Wallpaper brings a calm yet powerful ambiance, immersing your tab with Gojo’s luminous aura under moonlight.

Features:
Satoru Gojo Moon Glow Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension combines a stunning chrome wallpaper with practical tools for easy browsing. As one of the top chrome live wallpapers, it transforms your chrome background with Gojo’s tranquil yet commanding presence.

For more live wallpapers, visit Gameograf.com. Find similar options like: Hollow Purple Gojo Live Wallpaper, Sukuna Moonlight Live Wallpaper, Yuji Itadori Live Wallpaper, Megumi Fushiguro Night Glow Live Wallpaper, Nobara Kugisaki Live Wallpaper.
